 to the processing of Data."}),"Users have the right to object to the processing of their Data when it is carried out on the basis of a legal basis other than consent.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"When Personal Data is processed in the interest of the public, in the exercise of official authority vested in the Owner, or for the reasons of the Owner's legitimate interests, Users may object by providing a reason relating to their specific situation to justify the objection.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Users may object to the processing of their Personal Data for direct marketing purposes at any time and without providing a reason. Users may refer to the relevant sections of this document to determine if the Data Controller processes Personal Data for direct marketing purposes.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"Access their Data"}),"Users have the right to learn whether Data is being processed by the Owner, to obtain information about certain aspects of the processing, and to obtain a copy of the Data undergoing processing.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"We may, upon request, provide the User with additional and contextual information about specific Services or the collection and processing of Personal Data. Thus, more information about the collection or processing of Personal Data may be obtained from the Owner at any time.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"Verify and seek correction"}),"Users have the right to request that their Data is updated or corrected and to verify its accuracy. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"Restriction of Data processing"}),"Under certain conditions, Users have the right to restrict the processing of their Data. In this instance, the Owner will not use the Data for any other purpose than storage. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"Have their Personal Data deleted or removed"})," ","Under certain conditions, Users have the right to obtain the removal of their Data from the Owner. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"Receive their Data and transfer it to a different controller"})," ","Users have the right to receive their Data in a structured, commonly used, machine-readable format and, if technically feasible, to have it transmitted without restriction to another controller. This provision applies if the Data is processed by automated means on the basis of the User's consent, a contract to which the User is a party, or pre-contractual obligations. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"Lodge a complaint."}),"Users are permitted to file a complaint with their national data protection authority.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"5.2 Requests to exercise User rights should be sent to the Owner using the contact information listed in this document. These requests can be made free of charge and the Owner will respond as soon as possible, but no later than one month."]}),(0,r.jsx)("h3",{className:l.default.title,id:"cookies-and-tracking-technologies",children:"6. Do We Use Cookies and Other Tracking Technologies?"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:l.default.text,children:["We may use cookies and other tracking technologies to collect and store your information.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"A cookie is a small amount of information that’s downloaded to your computer or device when you visit our Website. We use a number of different cookies, including functional, performance, advertising, and social media or content cookies. Cookies make your browsing experience better by allowing the Website to remember your actions and preferences (such as login and region selection). This means you don’t have to re-enter this information each time you return to the Website or browse from one page to another. Cookies also provide information on how people use the Website, for instance, whether it’s their first time visiting or if they are frequent visitors. We use the following cookies to optimize your experience on the Website and to provide our services:"]}),(0,r.jsxs)("div",{className:l.default.table,children:[(0,r.jsxs)("div",{className:l.default.row,children:[(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.left,children:(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"Type of Cookie"})}),(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.right,children:(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"Purpose of Cookie"})})]}),(0,r.jsxs)("div",{className:l.default.row,children:[(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.left,children:"Necessary"}),(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.right,children:"Necessary Cookies are essential for the Site to display and perform properly. Necessary Cookies are used to identify you, prevent security risks, and allow you to perform account-related functions."})]}),(0,r.jsxs)("div",{className:l.default.row,children:[(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.left,children:"Preferences"}),(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.right,children:"Preferences Cookies are used to store preferences set by you and each user for their account, such as your language preferences. Preferences Cookies improve your experience using the Site."})]}),(0,r.jsxs)("div",{className:l.default.row,children:[(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.left,children:"Analytics and Performance"}),(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.right,children:"Analytics and Performance Cookies collect information on how you and other users interact with the Site. Often, this information is aggregated and is used to improve the Website."})]}),(0,r.jsxs)("div",{className:l.default.row,children:[(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.left,children:"Advertising"}),(0,r.jsx)("div",{className:l.default.right,children:"We may also use Cookies and web beacons, including those placed by Third Parties such as Google, to deliver Personalized Ads that may be of interest to you. We may also use a web beacon in email messages sent to track your response. Cookies and web beacons also help us and our Third-Party advertising partners ensure you do not see the same advertisements over and over and to identify and block unwanted ads. We also use these tracking tools to better understand your behaviors and browsing activities."})]})]}),(0,r.jsx)("h3",{className:l.default.title,id:"california-users",children:"7. Information for Users Residing in California"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:l.default.text,children:['This section of the document integrates and supplements the information contained in the rest of the Privacy Policy and is provided by us and, if applicable, our parent, subsidiaries, and affiliates (referred to collectively as "we", "us", and "our" for the purposes of this section). ',(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),'According to "The California Consumer Privacy Act of 2018," the provisions in this section apply to all Users who are consumers residing in the state of California, United States of America (Users are referred to below simply as "you", "your", "yours"), and these provisions supersede any other potentially divergent or conflicting provisions contained in the Privacy Policy for such consumers.',(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),'This section of the document employs the definition of "Personal Data" as defined in the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA). ',(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"This section summarizes the types of Personal Data that we have collected, disclosed, or sold, as well as the purposes for which we have done so. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"We collect Personal Data in the following categories:"}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"We have gathered the following types of Personal Data about you: identifiers, commercial data, internet data, geolocation data, and inferred data. We will not collect additional categories of Personal Data about you without your permission. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"What sources of Personal Data do we collect and how do we collect it?"}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"We collect the aforementioned categories of Personal Data from you, either directly or indirectly. For example, when you submit requests via any form on the Website, you directly provide your Personal Data. When you navigate the Website, you also provide Personal Data indirectly, as Personal Data about you is automatically observed and collected. Finally, we may collect your Personal Data from third parties who assist us with the Services or the operation of the Website and its features.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"How do we use the information we collect?"}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"For business purposes, we may disclose the Personal Data we collect about you to a third party. In this case, we enter into a written agreement with the third party, requiring the recipient to keep the Personal Data confidential and not use it for any purpose(s) other than those required to carry out the agreement. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"In order to provide you with our Services, we may also disclose your Personal Data to third parties if you explicitly ask or authorize us to do so. Please see the relevant section of this document for more information on the purposes of the processing. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"The sale of your personal data"})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),'For the purposes of this definition, "sale" refers to any "selling, renting, releasing, disclosing, making available, transferring, or otherwise communicating orally, in writing, or electronically, a consumer\'s Personal Data by a business to another business or a third party for monetary or other valuable consideration."'," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"This means, for instance, that a sale can occur if an application displays advertisements, does statistical analysis on the traffic or views, or employs social network plugins and similar tools.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"Your right to opt-out of the sale of personal data"}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"You have the option to not have your Personal Data sold. This implies that whenever you request that we cease selling your data, we will comply. These requests can be made at any time without filing a request that can be verified, by just following the guidelines below.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"Instructions for declining the sale of personal data"})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"If you would like more information or to exercise your right to opt-out of any online and offline sales conducted by the Website, please contact us using the information provided herein. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"What purposes do we have for using your Personal Data?"}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),'We may use your Personal Data to ensure the proper functioning of the Website ("commercial objectives"). In such instances, your Personal Data will be processed in a manner necessary and proportional to the business objective for which it was collected, and strictly within the parameters of compatible operational reasons. ',(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"We may also use your Personal Data for other purposes, such as marketing, as well as for abiding by the law and defending our rights before the competent authorities if our rights and interests are threatened or if we suffer an actual loss."," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"We will not use your Personal Data without your consent for irrelevant, unrelated, or incompatible reasons. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"Your privacy rights in California and how to exercise them?"})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"The right to transparency and portability"})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"You are permitted to request that we disclose: ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"The categories and sources of the Personal Data we collect about you, the purposes for which we use that information, and with whom we share it;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"In case of sale of Personal Data or disclosure for a commercial purpose, two separate lists where we disclose:"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"For sales, the Personal Data categories purchased by each category of recipient;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"For disclosures for a business purpose, the personal data categories obtained by each category of recipients."}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),'Providing this is technically feasible if we deliver our response electronically, the enclosed information will be "portable," meaning it will be delivered in an easily usable format that will allow you to transmit it to another entity without difficulty.'," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"The right to request that your Personal Data be deleted"})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"You have the right to request that we delete any of your Personal Data, subject to legal exceptions (such as, but not limited to, where the information is used to identify and repair errors on the Website, to detect security incidents and protect against fraudulent or illegal activities, to exercise certain rights, etc.). If no legal exception applies, we shall delete your Personal Data and direct our service partners to do the same in response to your request. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"How to exercise your legal rights?"})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"To exercise the rights stated above, you must submit a request that may be verified by contacting us using the information provided  herein. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"In order for us to reply to your request, we must know who you are. Therefore, you can only exercise the aforementioned rights by submitting a request that meets the following criteria: ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:l.default.list_item,children:"provide sufficient information to allow us to verify that you are the individual whose Personal Data we gathered or an authorized representative"}),"We will not respond to your request if we are unable to authenticate your identity and, by extension, that the Personal Data we know about you is accurate. If you are unable to submit a verifiable request in person, you may appoint a California Secretary of State-registered agent to act on your behalf. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"You can make a verified request on behalf of a minor under your parental authority if you are an adult. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"How and when do we anticipate handling your request?"})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Within 10 days, we will acknowledge receipt of your verifiable request and provide details on how it will be processed. We will respond within 45 days of receiving your inquiry. If we require additional time, we will explain the reasons why and the amount of time we require. Please be aware that we may require up to 90 days to fulfill your request. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Our disclosures will span the last twelve months. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"If we refuse your request, we will provide an explanation for our decision. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"We do not charge a fee to process or reply to your verifiable request unless it is plainly exorbitant or without justification. In such situations, we may charge a reasonable fee or decline to act. In either situation, we will disclose our choices and provide reasons."]}),(0,