ser will be solely liable under the local, state, national, or international laws and regulations, and “indemnity” provisions (Section 10) and any relevant provisions of this Agreement will apply in any of such cases."}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"harassing, threatening, defaming, abusing, or otherwise violating the legal rights of our personnel or other users, including but not limited to bullying, harassing, or attacking individuals or groups;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"carrying out illicit activities, such as the trading of forbidden products and/or services;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"contravening any applicable local, state, national, or international laws, as well as others' privacy or rights."}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"16.4 We reserve the right to suspend or terminate any account or restrict or delete any content that we deem to have a detrimental effect on the user experience or the safety of the public at large, as prohibited by our Acceptable Use Guidelines."]}),(0,r.jsx)("h3",{className:f.default.title,id:"upload-content-license",children:"17. Upload Content License"}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"17.1 License"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:["The content that you provide remains yours. Therefore, you retain any intellectual property rights that you have in your content, including but not limited to the intellectual property right in the creative content you produce by writing reviews or the right to share someone else's creative content if they have given you permission to do so. If your intellectual property rights restrict our use of your content, we need your permission. This license grants us permission in this regard. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"This license is worldwide, non-exclusive, assignable, sublicensable, transferable, and royalty-free. This means that it is applicable worldwide, there are no restrictions on the licensing of your content to others, and there are no fees associated with this license. ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Your content is covered by the license so long as it is protected by intellectual property rights. Your data security rights are unaffected.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"The following forms of content are excluded from coverage under this license:",(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"Publicly accessible information, such as corrections to the address of a local business, any information that is considered common knowledge and can be freely used by anyone without the need for a license."}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"Your comments (e.g., suggestions to improve our Services)."})]}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"17.2 Purpose"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:["This license's scope is limited to the operation of Services, allowing them to create new features and functions and operate as intended by their designers. This includes analyzing your content using automated systems and algorithms. As the content is transmitted, received, stored, and utilized, it is analyzed:",(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"to scan for illegal content, spam, or malware;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"to recognize data patterns used in functionalities such as storage optimization;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"to personalize our Services for you and to provide the Services such as usage recommendations or customized designs, content, and advertisements in the case of a free generator."})]}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"17.3 Rights"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:["Within the scope of the above-mentioned limited purposes, the following rights are granted to us via this license: ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"utilize your content solely for technical purposes, such as the storage of your content on our systems to make it accessible from anywhere or to ensure the compatibility of your content with our Services by reformatting your content;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"ensuring the public availability of your content if you have made it visible to others;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"sublicense these rights to other users to ensure that the Services function as intended, such as enabling you to share photos with other users;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:'sublicense these rights to our contractors under agreements that are consistent with these terms and doing so within the scope of the limited purposes described in the section titled "Purpose".'})]}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"17.4 Duration"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:["This license is valid for the period that your content is protected by intellectual property rights. This does not apply if you remove your content from our Services before the expiration date.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"The removal of any of your content from our Services that is covered by this license will cause our systems to stop making this content publicly accessible within a reasonable timeframe. There are the following exceptions:",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"you have shared your content with others via a static QR code that links to a third-party website before removing it;"}),(0,r.jsx)("span",{className:f.default.list_item,children:"it is possible that search engines and so-called web archives will continue to find and display your content as part of their search results if you make your content accessible through the services of other companies."})]}),(0,r.jsx)("h3",{className:f.default.title,id:"cancellation-policy",children:"18. Cancellation policy"}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"18.1 The right to cancel the subscription"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:["You may cancel your subscription at any time without providing a reason by logging into your account or contacting us using the contact information and form provided below. Your cancellation will take effect at the end of your current paid term.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"To exercise the right of cancellation, the User must inform Us"," ",(0,r.jsx)("a",{href:"mailto:support@qrfast.com",className:f.default.innerLink,children:"(support@qrfast.com)"}),"of his/her decision to cancel his/her subscription by a clear statement (e.g., a letter sent via post, fax, or email; see the below model cancelation form for this purpose). The User may also electronically complete and submit the model cancellation form or another clear declaration on his/her account on the Site.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"All purchases of the Services are final, and no refund shall be provided due to cancellation except as specifically noted in these Terms below."})]}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"18.2 Right of withdrawal and Refund Policy for EU and UK Residents Only"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:["You have the right to withdraw from this Agreement within 14 days without giving any reason. The withdrawal period will expire after 14 days from the day of the conclusion of the contract. To exercise the right of withdrawal, you must inform us as specified in the Section 18.4 below. To meet the withdrawal deadline, it is sufficient for you to send your communication concerning your exercise of the right of withdrawal before the withdrawal period has expired. You may use the model withdrawal form in Section 18.4, but it is not obligatory.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"As mentioned above, if the User is a customer residing in the EU and the UK, they have the right to withdraw from the Agreement for digital content purchases within 14 days from the purchase date. However, this right applies only until the moment the actual download or streaming of the digital content begins.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"In the case of contracts for the delivery of digital content not provided on a physical medium, your right of withdrawal will expire prematurely if you expressly consent to us commencing the performance of the contract prior to the expiration of the withdrawal period and acknowledge that you will lose your right of withdrawal upon the commencement of the contract’s performance.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"If the User downloads or streams digital content during a free trial, the purchase date is considered the date on which the digital content was first accessed (downloaded or streamed), regardless of whether the User has subscribed to a full plan at that time. Therefore, if the free trial grants access to the same digital content as the paid subscription and the User agrees to waive his/her right of withdrawal when s/he starts downloading, s/he will not be entitled to a refund after purchasing the full subscription plan.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"In other words, the right to withdrawal from the Agreement will not apply if the User has expressly agreed to receive or download the digital content within the withdrawal period and has expressly waived their right of withdrawal. During the download or streaming process of the digital content, the User will be asked to confirm that they waive their right of withdrawal, making them ineligible for any refund.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"If the User invokes their right of withdrawal within 14 days and before starting the download or streaming process, the amount paid will be refunded within 14 days from the declaration of withdrawal. We will carry out such reimbursement using the same means of payment as you used for the initial transaction, unless you have expressly agreed otherwise; in any event, you will not incur any fees as a result of such reimbursement."]}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"18.3 Refund Policy for New Users due to Access Failure"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:["If a new User completes payment for a full subscription and subsequently fails to receive access to the Services due to the inability to access the account, a non-functional QR code, or a non-functional dashboard, the User must notify Us in writing at ",(0,r.jsx)("a",{href:"mailto:support@qrfast.com",className:f.default.innerLink,children:"support@qrfast.com"})," within twenty-four (24) hours of the payment. The notification must include the User’s email address, User/Customer ID, invoice number, payment date, and amount paid. Failure to provide complete and timely notice shall constitute a waiver of all remedies under this sub-section 18.3.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Upon receipt of a valid notice, We will use commercially reasonable efforts to investigate and restore access within forty-eight (48) hours. If access is not successfully restored within that timeframe, the User will be entitled to a full refund of all fees paid for the Services. Any applicable refund will be issued to the original method of payment within five (5) business days following confirmation of the User’s eligibility. Once the applicable refund has been issued, the paid subscription plan will be automatically cancelled, and the User will not be required to submit an additional cancellation/withdrawal form.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"This refund policy applies exclusively to new Users who have registered and subscribed to the full version of our Services and have experienced a complete failure of access. Thus, this narrow refund remedy supersedes the standard no-refund rule during the current billing cycle, but only in cases of access failure by new Users as defined in this sub-section 18.3. For all other Users, including ongoing subscribers, the general provisions of this Agreement shall apply. In particular, We do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free operation of the Services, although we strive to maintain high standards of availability and functionality. We also reserve the right, but not the obligation, to correct any errors or omissions in any portion of the Site at any time without prior notice."]}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"18.4 Model cancellation/withdrawal form"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:["Please complete and return this form only if you wish to withdraw from the contract:",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"To: ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"QR Fast,",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"51 Bracken Rd, ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Sandyford, Dublin, D18 CV48,",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Ireland",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Email:"," ",(0,r.jsx)("a",{href:"mailto:support@qrfast.com",className:f.default.innerLink,children:"support@qrfast.com"})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{})," ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"I/we (*) hereby withdraw from the contract for the purchase of the following items (*)/provision of the following service (*).",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Ordered on (*) and received on (*)",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Name of the User(s): ",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Address of the User(s):",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Signature(s) of the User(s) (only in case of paper communication):",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Date:",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"(*) Delete where irrelevant.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("b",{children:"Note: Submitting this form will cancel your subscription for the next billing period. As stated in sub-section 18.1 of the Agreement, please note that all purchases of the Services are final, and no refund shall be provided due to cancellation except as specifically noted herein."})]}),(0,r.jsx)("h4",{className:f.default.subtitle,children:"18.5 Deletion of the User’s account upon cancellation"}),(0,r.jsx)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:"After the paid subscription plan is cancelled, the User’s account will remain accessible until the conclusion of your current paid subscription term. After the current paid subscription term, the User’s data will become temporarily unavailable until s/he switches to a new paid subscription plan. If the User does not subscribe to a new paid subscription plan within a 90-day period after his/her current paid subscription plan expires, We retain the right to terminate the Agreement and delete the User's account at our sole discretion."}),(0,r.jsx)("h3",{className:f.default.title,id:"personal-data-protection",children:"19. Personal Data Protection"}),(0,r.jsxs)("p",{className:f.default.text,children:[" We are dedicated to protecting your privacy and securing your Personal Data. Our practices adhere to the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) (EU) 2016/679 and all applicable national data protection laws. We process Personal Data lawfully, fairly, and transparently, exclusively for purposes compatible with those detailed in our Privacy Policy. Further information on how we process personal data, including your rights under the GDPR, can be found in our Privacy Policy: ",(0,r.jsx)(o.default,{href:"/policy",className:(0,c.default)(f.default.innerLink,f.default.pageLink),children:"qrfast.com/policy."}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard your information against unauthorized processing, loss, destruction, or damage. Access to Personal Data is strictly limited to authorized personnel and service providers who need it to perform their duties and are bound by strict confidentiality obligations. Personal Data is retained only as long as necessary to fulfill the collection purposes or as required by applicable law.",(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),(0,r.jsx)("br",{}),"Please contact us at ",(0,r.jsx)("a",{href:"mailto:support@qrfast.com",className:f.default.innerLink,children:"support@qrfast.com"})," for more information about our privacy practices or if you have any questions."]})]})})]})},features:{navigation:{about:!1,contact:!1},site:{}},meta:{description:"QR Fast for Wi-fi,Location,Social media,URL,vCard,Text,email,sms,images,phone,pdf,word,and more. Add sticker , logo, colors, frames, shapes and download in high print quality. Get your free QR Codes now! qrcodecreator Qr Fast qrcode qr code",keywords:"Qrcode , qrcode , qr code , barcode , wi-fi , social , creator , generator , bestqrcode , best qrcode",twitterHandle:"@qrfast",siteName:"qrfast.com",siteURL:"https://qrfast.com"},data:{contact:[{id:"email",title:"Email",Icon:p.HiOutlineMail,link:"mailto:support@qrfast.com",linkText:"support@qrfast.com"},{id:"location",title:"Location",Icon:p.HiOutlineLocationMarker,link:"https://maps.app.goo.gl/dyFerdD8JTC5kaMw9",linkText:"51 Bracken Rd, Sandyford, Dublin, D18 CV48, Ireland"}]}}};e.s(["BRANDS",0,g],877294)}]);